{"id": "1492518150627917864", "channel_id": "1492518042431918212", "author_id": "544721299197394963", "author_name": "shio2311", "content": "Ultra Realm\n+Chorus\n\nPsyche Surge:\n+ Realm Mastery\n+ Death Resistance\n\nTalents:\n+Gain 5 STR for each card discarded with exalt or command cards.\n+Soulforge: At the start of the battle, discard any amount of cards and draw the same amount. STR gained from Titor is doubled.\n\nEnlightens:\n+E1: Gain 10 aliemus for each card discarded with exalt or command cards.\n+E2: Strike enjoys 3x STR bonus and Defense obtains shield twice and gain Leap: reduce cost -1.\n+E3: I. Must. Scream. temporarily reduces all enemy STR.\n\n+Exalt: Digital Assimilation\nDiscard from your hand up to the number of cards in your ultra space, select and move cards from ultra space to hand up to the number discarded with exhaust.\n\n+Overexalt: H▲Tϵ.!i\nDeal fixed piercing damage to all enemies, which enjoys a 5x STR bonus. For each card moved, +1 hit. Attach retain to all cards moved.\n\nCards:\n+Rouse: Temporal Anomaly\n 2 Cost\nGain 50 Aliemus\nGain 20 STR. The next Leap and Quasar this turn is guaranteed to trigger.\n\n+Command 1: Mnestic Serum\nCost 1\nObtain shield and discard up to 4 and draw the same amount, for each discard gain 5% Temporary Crit Rate for all units.\nQuasar: Gain 20 Aliemus. \nAftershock: Gain 1 Arithmetica\n\n+Command 2: I. Must. Scream.\nCost 3\nDeal damage 3 times to random enemies, which enjoys a 3x STR bonus.\nEach hit Crit Rate +50%\nReduce cost -1 each time aftershock is triggered.\nRetain.\nQuasar: Gain 20 Aliemus. \nAftershock: Gain 1 Arithmetica\n\n+Strike:\nCost 1\nDeal damage. Aftershock: Gain 1 Arithmetica.\n\n+Defense:\nCost 1\nObtain shield. Aftershock: Gain 1 Arithmetica.", "timestamp": "2026-04-11T13:34:16.756000+00:00", "thread_id": "1492518042431918212"}
